  23 Apr 2005; MATSUU Takuto <matsuu@gentoo.org> -otcl-1.8-r1.ebuild,
  -otcl-1.8-r2.ebuild, otcl-1.9.ebuild:
  Fixed parallel make problem, Bug 90149.
  Removed old versions.

